ial bodies, it completely remakes them with new textures and terrain.\u00A0 It also adds some new bodies.\u00A0 JNSQ is technically suppose to be 1/4 real scale, which works out to be about 2.7x stock scale.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aelfhe1m","CreatedById":142910,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-07T09:08:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022204201\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7059983303\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/195569-181-191-rescale-continued-v100/?do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:194px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr there is a new mod in development that looks like it might be promising:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022230140\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4734519388\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/223641-1125-celestial-rescale-v030-rescale-the-stock-system/?do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:194px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}